        </row>
        <row>
          <cell><m>0</m></cell>
          <cell><m>-5</m></cell>
        </row>
      </tabular>
    </table>

  </sidebyside>
  <p>
    We do not need to compute any points to the left of the vertex.  We can use the symmetry of the parabola across the line <m>x=-3</m> to infer three points to the left of the of the vertex.  These three point have been added to <xref ref="parabolas-standard-form-table-2">Table</xref> and a graph of the parabola is shown in <xref ref="parabolas-standard-form-figure-4">Figure</xref>.
  </p>
